msgid "Rollback & Cleanup"
msgstr "回滚与清理"

msgid "Warning: Rollback operations will remove configurations created by this plugin. Proceed with caution."
msgstr "警告：回滚操作将移除本插件创建的配置。请谨慎操作。"

msgid "Are you sure you want to undo all initialization? This will remove all plugin-created configurations (interface, zone, OpenClash rules, nftables rules)."
msgstr "确定要撤销所有初始化吗？这将移除所有插件创建的配置（接口、区域、OpenClash 规则、nftables 规则）。"

