msgstr "清除 nftables 规则"

msgid "WARNING: This will remove ALL plugin-created configurations, rules, and restore backups. Are you sure?"
msgstr "警告：这将移除所有插件创建的配置、规则并恢复备份。确定继续？"

msgid "All plugin configurations and rules have been cleaned up."
msgstr "所有插件配置和规则已清理。"

